            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>This is the tombstone … died … days in the month Ab(?) in the [six]th year of the
                    seven year cycle, the year three [hund]red [and n]inety one years of the
                    destruction of the Sanctuary. Peace</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>391 E.D.S, 6th S.Y. is equivalent to 460 CE.</p>
            </div>
